          <img alt="Julia Veldkamp. Foto: Isabella Rozendaal (voor De Correspondent)" data-src="https://dynamic.decorrespondent.nl/ff-1442634310/media/{breakpoint-name}/55fc011cbc4aa9131769641.jpg" class="" src="https://dynamic.decorrespondent.nl/ff-1442634310/media/1920/55fc011cbc4aa9131769641.jpg">
